  83:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma_ex.c ****                     The DMA channel keep an empty area, between each 2 consecutive blocks transmitt
  84:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma_ex.c **** 
